===Etymology===
{{och-l|彤|red}} could be a variant of {{och-l|紅}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). May be related to {{och-l|虹|id=1+3|rainbow}}.

Originally referred to lighter shades of red; gradually replaced {{zh-l|赤|red}} as the basic color term for "red".

